a3264fe53ff8c06c1f7dc7c7937d390ac11b3481.name: WESTsuperpreis ticket
a3264fe53ff8c06c1f7dc7c7937d390ac11b3481.conditionsSummary: Valid on the selected travel date on the selected train. The booked ticket can only be used once on another WESTbahn train in the booked direction on the selected day of validity for an additional fee on top of the WESTstandard price. Cancellation is possible up to one day before the departure for a fee of 25% of the ticket price, and will be at least 4.99. In any case, cancellation is possible up to 15 minutes after purchase.
